{"tid":1548174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際戰線] 即時英文翻譯文宣，快啲同我share出去！","createTime":"2019-09-07T02:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:20:53.000Z","uid":285915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0509482b833116f75e4529eaa3025611a6aa98c9","tid":1548174,"uid":285915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:45:38.000Z","msg":"難得今日入機場，我哋又有機會重啟外國戰線。小弟之前已經開過po<br />\n（跪求幫推） 其實香港有班人好努力做翻譯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545086</a><br />\n，不過好多人都唔知個po係關於翻譯英文文宣，希望今次可以推爆佢。難得有手足即時翻譯新聞，我哋一定要幫佢地share出去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近好似好多人話英文嘅文宣唔夠，又話鬼佬想睇到啲翻譯左嘅新聞。其實又班香港人已經做緊架啦，我哋網站叫<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=0d58feb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com</a>，我哋每日都會將香港嘅新聞翻譯再放上fb，tg，同埋twitter。小弟p牌冇得推po，唯有靠大家幫手推到外國人都知香港發生咩事。<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FCommunity-Organization%2FBeWater-HK-2406628919558580%2F&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=ad9f34ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhkg%2F%3Figshid%3Dwe1lffxlqh9f&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=993d50db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fbewaterhkg&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=00761515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Srv8Mg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrv8Mg7.jpg&h=51ec2705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbwr60J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcbwr60J.png&h=b32d16e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D60sRsp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD60sRsp.png&h=7cdcccdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWQgKNp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWQgKNp.png&h=1c77cc38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTGGVT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTGGVT5.png&h=1eacf0ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bc0aa4700bc87a5731a7e1528633ed05ab993c7","tid":1548174,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cb1e901f441cc4ccd1a8596cffbe7b1430553ee","tid":1548174,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"竟然無人推<br />\n請問有無民主人權法案前因後果英文懶人包<br />\n我想share俾d鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2388642992d738f62a990e004405fe150653eaf6","tid":1548174,"uid":285915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb1e901f441cc4ccd1a8596cffbe7b1430553ee","tid":1548174,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"竟然無人推<br />\n請問有無民主人權法案前因後果英文懶人包<br />\n我想share俾d鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"你幫下手啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc94d84ca044e52cf9fd0f67e524af999cbbd44","tid":1548174,"uid":250889,"like":0,"dislik